description._content: Collection: Crowe (Milburn J.) Photograph Album Call number: PI/2005.0015 System ID: 94508. Link to the catalog The Crowe (Milburn J.) album. (top left) indexed as: B. T. Green notes: Photographs on page 12 (image 18) rearranged or missing. This may be M. R. Montgomery. photographer: H. J. Herrick, Vicksburg, Mississippi (top right) indexed as: M. R. Montgomery notes: “M. R. Montgomery.” Photographs on page 12 rearranged or missing. This may be Benjamin Titus Green (cofounder of Mound Bayou) or George W. Boyd (a planter at Davis Bend). photographer: H. J. Herrick, Vicksburg, Mississippi (bottom left) indexed as: George Boyde notes: No photograph at the bottom left of the page. (bottom right) indexed as: Stella Montgomery notes: “G. Boyd?” Photographs on page 12 rearranged or missing. This may be Estella Montgomery (Isaiah's daughter). photographer: A. L. Blanks, Vicksburg, Mississippi Please see our profile page for information on ordering. Credit: Courtesy of the Mississippi Department of Archives and History
